756
00:22:10,620 --> 00:22:11,820
 kako su fratri reagirali

757
00:22:11,820 --> 00:22:13,400
 u župi?

758
00:22:13,400 --> 00:22:15,940
 Počet ću s drugim pitanjem.

759
00:22:15,940 --> 00:22:16,180
 Može.

760
00:22:17,760 --> 00:22:18,240
 ovako,

761
00:22:18,240 --> 00:22:20,280
 ja sam,

762
00:22:20,280 --> 00:22:20,820
 mislim,

763
00:22:20,820 --> 00:22:24,780
 sve te informacije ja dobijem od svog oca,

764
00:22:24,780 --> 00:22:25,920
 kako su oni reagirali,

765
00:22:25,920 --> 00:22:26,420
 tako,

766
00:22:26,420 --> 00:22:27,020
 ovaj,

767
00:22:27,020 --> 00:22:28,440
 i mi smo to više

768
00:22:28,440 --> 00:22:29,760
 uvijek komentirali

769
00:22:29,760 --> 00:22:30,660
 kroz neku šalu,

770
00:22:30,660 --> 00:22:31,300
 u smislu,

771
00:22:31,300 --> 00:22:33,320
 majde, Frano,

772
00:22:33,320 --> 00:22:35,300
 oni ti nude bolje uvijete,

773
00:22:35,300 --> 00:22:36,780
 kao pređi k njima,

774
00:22:36,780 --> 00:22:37,960
 majde, Frano,

775
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:38,820
 ti si hercegovat,

776
00:22:38,820 --> 00:22:39,860
 kućeš u Salesijanci,

777
00:22:39,860 --> 00:22:40,740
 otkud Salesijanci,

778
00:22:40,740 --> 00:22:41,400
 i tako dalje,

779
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:42,440
 ovaj,

780
00:22:42,440 --> 00:22:43,900
 rekao bih da su se iznenadili,

781
00:22:43,900 --> 00:22:46,320
 pogotovo zato jer je prva osoba

782
00:22:46,320 --> 00:22:47,540
 koju se ja rekao

783
00:22:47,540 --> 00:22:48,280
 da razmišljamo poziv,

784
00:22:48,280 --> 00:22:49,220
 je bilan Franjevac,

785
00:22:49,220 --> 00:22:51,260
 na jednoj ispovjedi,

786
00:22:51,260 --> 00:22:52,140
 e,

787
00:22:52,140 --> 00:22:53,860
 ja sam njemu rekao tu stvar,

788
00:22:53,860 --> 00:22:54,260
 i,

789
00:22:54,260 --> 00:22:56,480
 on je bio tako radostan,

790
00:22:56,480 --> 00:22:58,140
 što sam mu ja rekao to,

791
00:22:58,140 --> 00:23:00,380
 da je on meni kazao,

792
00:23:00,380 --> 00:23:01,780
 da je zaboravio reći da dođiš k njima,

793
00:23:01,780 --> 00:23:02,160
 u smislu,

794
00:23:02,160 --> 00:23:02,700
 on je meni rekao,

795
00:23:02,700 --> 00:23:04,300
 evo, ti reci roditeljima,

796
00:23:04,300 --> 00:23:07,040
 napiši modu i ulaziš i gotovo,

797
00:23:07,040 --> 00:23:08,420
 nema razlučivanja,

798
00:23:08,420 --> 00:23:08,720
 nema,

799
00:23:08,720 --> 00:23:10,400
 jel ti imaš poziv u istinu,

800
00:23:10,400 --> 00:23:11,320
 nemaš i tako dalje,

801
00:23:11,320 --> 00:23:12,440
 ovaj,

802
00:23:12,440 --> 00:23:13,060
 tako da je,

803
00:23:13,440 --> 00:23:14,700
 taj Franjevac je bio

804
00:23:14,700 --> 00:23:15,820
 pomalo iznenađen,

805
00:23:15,820 --> 00:23:17,100
 to je bio Frajozo Zovko,

806
00:23:17,100 --> 00:23:19,060
 poznati fratar,

807
00:23:19,060 --> 00:23:21,180
 on je bio malo iznenađen

808
00:23:21,180 --> 00:23:21,520
 kad je,

809
00:23:21,520 --> 00:23:22,680
 kad je poslije skužio

810
00:23:22,680 --> 00:23:23,560
 delimu Salizijance,

811
00:23:23,560 --> 00:23:25,180
 a prvo sam njemu rekao,

812
00:23:25,180 --> 00:23:25,460
 jeli,

813
00:23:25,460 --> 00:23:27,440
 tako da više je to bilo

814
00:23:27,440 --> 00:23:28,200
 kroz šalu

815
00:23:28,200 --> 00:23:29,900
 i svi su mi oni velika podrška

816
00:23:29,900 --> 00:23:31,540
 na mome,

817
00:23:31,540 --> 00:23:32,280
 na mome putu,

818
00:23:32,320 --> 00:23:33,260
 za sigurno mi je bilo

819
00:23:33,260 --> 00:23:33,820
 iznenađenje,

820
00:23:33,820 --> 00:23:35,300
 jer sam iz Franjevečke župe

821
00:23:35,300 --> 00:23:36,220
 i jer sam iz Hercegovine,

822
00:23:36,220 --> 00:23:38,540
 a što se tiče,

823
00:23:38,540 --> 00:23:39,880
 čekaj,

824
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:40,160
 ponovim,

825
00:23:40,160 --> 00:23:40,620
 prvo pitanje.

826
00:23:40,620 --> 00:23:41,380
 Zašto baš Salizijanci?

827
00:23:41,380 --> 00:23:42,280
 A, zašto baš Salizijanci?

828
00:23:42,280 --> 00:23:43,420
 Ovako,

829
00:23:43,420 --> 00:23:44,000
 ja Salizijanci...

830
00:23:44,000 --> 00:23:44,660
 Imali su koši

831
00:23:44,660 --> 00:23:45,100
 ispred crkve,

832
00:23:45,100 --> 00:23:45,760
 to je sigurno?

833
00:23:45,760 --> 00:23:46,700
 Pa to je jedan prednost,

834
00:23:46,700 --> 00:23:47,240
 za sigurno,

835
00:23:47,240 --> 00:23:47,520
 da,

836
00:23:47,520 --> 00:23:49,460
 ja Salizijanci nisam poznavao

837
00:23:49,460 --> 00:23:50,760
 do svoje 15.

838
00:23:50,760 --> 00:23:51,600
 16. godine,

839
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:52,820
 prvi Salizijanci

840
00:23:52,820 --> 00:23:53,360
 kojeg sam upoznao

841
00:23:53,360 --> 00:23:54,520
 bio je Don Damir Stović,

842
00:23:55,800 --> 00:23:56,920
 ja sam kao srednjoškolac

843
00:23:56,920 --> 00:23:57,800
 krenuo na njegove

844
00:23:57,800 --> 00:23:59,660
 kateheze za studente.

845
00:23:59,660 --> 00:24:01,520
 Moja sestra je išla prva,

846
00:24:01,520 --> 00:24:03,300
 ona je bila oduševljena

847
00:24:03,300 --> 00:24:03,980
 i rekla mi je,

848
00:24:03,980 --> 00:24:04,520
 Frano,

849
00:24:04,520 --> 00:24:05,360
 ti moraš doći

850
00:24:05,360 --> 00:24:06,600
 poslušat ove stvari.

851
00:24:06,600 --> 00:24:07,980
 Ja sam u trećem srednje

852
00:24:07,980 --> 00:24:09,300
 krenuo

853
00:24:09,300 --> 00:24:10,200
 zajedno s njom

854
00:24:10,200 --> 00:24:11,100
 i čak sam nekad,

855
00:24:11,100 --> 00:24:13,100
 priznajem to javno,

856
00:24:13,100 --> 00:24:14,900
 bježao sa zadnjeg sata

857
00:24:14,900 --> 00:24:15,980
 da stignem,

858
00:24:15,980 --> 00:24:16,260
 dakle,

859
00:24:16,260 --> 00:24:17,020
 iz Sesveta

860
00:24:17,020 --> 00:24:17,820
 do Save

861
00:24:17,820 --> 00:24:18,780
 na drugi kraj grada

862
00:24:18,780 --> 00:24:19,960
 da stignem na Vjeronauk.

863
00:24:19,960 --> 00:24:20,960
 Javnim prevozom, naravno.

864
00:24:20,960 --> 00:24:21,320
 Tako je,

865
00:24:21,420 --> 00:24:22,080
 javnim prevozom.

866
00:24:22,080 --> 00:24:23,900
 Šta mi je tu prijučio?

867
00:24:23,900 --> 00:24:24,620
 Prvi put sam vidio

868
00:24:24,620 --> 00:24:25,540
 svećenika,

869
00:24:25,540 --> 00:24:26,380
 prvo,

870
00:24:26,380 --> 00:24:27,840
 koji

871
00:24:27,840 --> 00:24:30,460
 okuplja toliko mladih,

872
00:24:30,460 --> 00:24:31,920
 drugo,

873
00:24:31,920 --> 00:24:32,860
 vidio sam

874
00:24:32,860 --> 00:24:33,620
 toliko mladih

875
00:24:33,620 --> 00:24:34,320
 na jednom mjestu.

876
00:24:34,320 --> 00:24:35,160
 Meni je do tada

877
00:24:35,160 --> 00:24:36,280
 pojam crkve bilo

878
00:24:36,280 --> 00:24:37,540
 bakice

879
00:24:37,540 --> 00:24:38,760
 i ljudi

880
00:24:38,760 --> 00:24:39,400
 koji

881
00:24:39,400 --> 00:24:40,620
 u vjeri traže

882
00:24:40,620 --> 00:24:41,620
 neku utjehu.

883
00:24:41,620 --> 00:24:42,280
 I to je to.

884
00:24:42,280 --> 00:24:43,420
 To je bio

885
00:24:43,420 --> 00:24:45,780
 moj pojam crkve.

886
00:24:45,780 --> 00:24:47,320
 No ja sam se iznadio

887
00:24:47,320 --> 00:24:47,580
 kad sam vidio

888
00:24:47,580 --> 00:24:48,300
 200-300

889
00:24:48,300 --> 00:24:50,180
 mladih ljudi

890
00:24:50,180 --> 00:24:50,880
 koji utorkom,

891
00:24:50,960 --> 00:24:51,360
 srijedom,

892
00:24:51,360 --> 00:24:52,920
 dolaze slušat svećenika

893
00:24:52,920 --> 00:24:53,560
 koji njima govori

894
00:24:53,560 --> 00:24:54,760
 na primjer o teologiji tijela.

895
00:24:54,760 --> 00:24:56,880
 Njegov žar,

896
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:58,280
 njegova

897
00:24:58,280 --> 00:24:59,880
 njegova revnost,

898
00:24:59,880 --> 00:25:01,060
 to me je jako privuklo.

899
00:25:01,060 --> 00:25:02,120
 I onda poslije sam

900
00:25:02,120 --> 00:25:03,500
 došao do jednog drugog

901
00:25:03,500 --> 00:25:03,920
 salizijanska

902
00:25:03,920 --> 00:25:04,260
 koji je postao

903
00:25:04,260 --> 00:25:04,880
 moj duhovnik.

904
00:25:04,880 --> 00:25:06,240
 On mi je dao

905
00:25:06,240 --> 00:25:07,120
 knjigu o Dombosku

906
00:25:07,120 --> 00:25:08,100
 pod nazivom

907
00:25:08,100 --> 00:25:09,100
 Ukrali ste mi srce.

908
00:25:09,100 --> 00:25:10,680
 I ja sam tu knjigu

909
00:25:10,680 --> 00:25:11,640
 progutao

910
00:25:11,640 --> 00:25:12,520
 u tjedan dana.

911
00:25:12,520 --> 00:25:13,720
 Ima 300 nešto stranice.

912
00:25:13,720 --> 00:25:14,240
 Ja se sjećam,

913
00:25:14,240 --> 00:25:14,820
 ja sam mi je čitao

914
00:25:14,820 --> 00:25:15,740
 do jedan, dva u noći.

915
00:25:15,840 --> 00:25:16,320
 preporučaš.

916
00:25:16,320 --> 00:25:17,440
 Preporučam, da.

917
00:25:17,440 --> 00:25:19,240
 I kroz tu knjigu

918
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:20,240
 sam jednostavno

919
00:25:20,240 --> 00:25:21,200
 se oduševio

920
00:25:21,200 --> 00:25:21,880
 Domboskom,

921
00:25:21,880 --> 00:25:22,920
 njegovim likom,

922
00:25:22,920 --> 00:25:23,840
 njegovim životom

923
00:25:23,840 --> 00:25:25,460
 i prepoznao sam sebe

924
00:25:25,460 --> 00:25:26,080
 u njemu

925
00:25:26,080 --> 00:25:27,460
 i vidio sam da

926
00:25:27,460 --> 00:25:28,560
 ono što je on živio

927
00:25:28,560 --> 00:25:30,000
 želim i ja zapravo

928
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:31,000
 živjeti.

929
00:25:31,080 --> 00:25:35,800
 Ti si iz Dubrovnika.

930
00:25:35,800 --> 00:25:37,840
 Tako, odrasto Dubrovnik.

931
00:25:37,840 --> 00:25:39,080
 Dole ima Salesijanice.

932
00:25:39,080 --> 00:25:41,120
 Bili su, bili su Salesijanci

933
00:25:41,120 --> 00:25:41,820
 u Mokošici

934
00:25:41,820 --> 00:25:44,020
 ali nije to baš bila

935
00:25:44,020 --> 00:25:45,700
 najsretnija priča

936
00:25:45,700 --> 00:25:46,660
 jer nekako uvijek je tamo

937
00:25:46,660 --> 00:25:47,660
 falilo prostora.

938
00:25:47,660 --> 00:25:49,020
 Znači tamo nije bilo

939
00:25:49,020 --> 00:25:49,560
 ni crkve,

940
00:25:49,560 --> 00:25:50,820
 je bio neki postovni prostor

941
00:25:50,820 --> 00:25:51,620
 koji se uredio.

942
00:25:51,620 --> 00:25:53,020
 Nije bilo dvorišta,

943
00:25:53,020 --> 00:25:54,020
 nije bilo oratorija,

944
00:25:54,020 --> 00:25:55,300
 bilo jako, jako teško

945
00:25:55,300 --> 00:25:56,300
 za nas Salesijanci

946
00:25:56,300 --> 00:25:57,260
 tako da su Salesijanci

947
00:25:57,260 --> 00:25:58,380
 bili kratko tamo

948
00:25:58,380 --> 00:25:59,400
 i nisu uspjeli

949
00:25:59,400 --> 00:26:00,120
 baš previše.

950
00:26:00,240 --> 00:26:00,920
 to je bila župa

951
00:26:00,920 --> 00:26:01,480
 dom moji.

952
00:26:01,480 --> 00:26:03,260
 A ja sam bio u fratarskoj župi

953
00:26:03,260 --> 00:26:04,420
 isto, ovaj, klasika,

954
00:26:04,420 --> 00:26:05,080
 evo, tako da.

955
00:26:05,080 --> 00:26:07,600
 Dovori, otkud baš Salesijanci?

956
00:26:07,600 --> 00:26:09,180
 Pa, evo, znači,

957
00:26:09,180 --> 00:26:10,700
 otkud baš Salesijanci?

958
00:26:10,700 --> 00:26:12,260
 Evo, prije svega

959
00:26:12,260 --> 00:26:12,880
 što

960
00:26:12,880 --> 00:26:15,540
 vidim da, evo,

961
00:26:15,540 --> 00:26:17,000
 mojoj duši

962
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:18,620
 odgovara ta duhovnost.

963
00:26:18,620 --> 00:26:19,380
 Evo, vidim da me Bog

964
00:26:19,380 --> 00:26:19,860
 za to,

965
00:26:19,860 --> 00:26:21,460
 na to poziva.

966
00:26:21,460 --> 00:26:23,220
 Salesijanska duhovnost

967
00:26:23,220 --> 00:26:23,780
 koja je dosta

968
00:26:23,780 --> 00:26:25,680
 pitka, jednostavna,

969
00:26:25,680 --> 00:26:27,480
 radosna, direktna.

970
00:26:27,480 --> 00:26:28,560
 Evo, to nekako odgovara

971
00:26:28,560 --> 00:26:29,920
 mojoj duši,

972
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:30,960
 naravno, to poslanje

973
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:31,580
 koje mi imamo,

974
00:26:31,580 --> 00:26:32,080
 ovaj,

975
00:26:32,080 --> 00:26:32,900
 mladi,

976
00:26:32,900 --> 00:26:33,360
 uvijek sam,

977
00:26:33,360 --> 00:26:34,620
 uvijek sam volio djecu,

978
00:26:34,620 --> 00:26:35,880
 uvijek sam volio biti s mladima,

979
00:26:35,880 --> 00:26:36,620
 u nekom društvu,

980
00:26:36,620 --> 00:26:37,240
 tako, s njima.

981
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:39,060
 biteljski duh koji je za nas

982
00:26:39,060 --> 00:26:39,680
 jako važan,

983
00:26:39,680 --> 00:26:40,900
 koji mi gajimo Salesijanci,

984
00:26:40,900 --> 00:26:41,940
 evo, to sve nekako mi je

985
00:26:41,940 --> 00:26:42,760
 jako puno, ovaj,

986
00:26:42,760 --> 00:26:44,040
 evo, baš,

987
00:26:44,040 --> 00:26:46,120
 baš sam prepoznal da je to ono,

988
00:26:46,120 --> 00:26:47,640
 ono, da je to ono što je za mene.

989
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:49,840
 I onda, evo, nekako u Zagrebu

990
00:26:49,840 --> 00:26:51,700
 sam opoznao, evo, zanimljivo i ja,

991
00:26:51,700 --> 00:26:53,360
 i ja preko Dondamira Stojića,

992
00:26:53,360 --> 00:26:54,460
 evo, i to isto, ovaj,

993
00:26:54,460 --> 00:26:56,960
 jedna sličnost među mene i Frane,

994
00:26:56,960 --> 00:26:57,860
 kako sam ja došao

995
00:26:57,860 --> 00:26:59,120
 do Dondamira Stojića.

996
00:26:59,200 --> 00:27:00,060
 mene su moje rodice,

997
00:27:00,060 --> 00:27:02,660
 tada dok sam se još malo

998
00:27:02,660 --> 00:27:03,360
 kao obraćao,

999
00:27:03,360 --> 00:27:05,460
 i tad sam živio to vrijeme u Dubravi,

1000
00:27:05,460 --> 00:27:07,060
 i tamo sam bio skroz lošom društvu

1001
00:27:07,060 --> 00:27:07,760
 i sve ovo ono,

1002
00:27:07,760 --> 00:27:08,760
 one su mene malo po malo

1003
00:27:08,760 --> 00:27:09,400
 božju povijedu,

1004
00:27:09,400 --> 00:27:10,240
 na susrete,

1005
00:27:10,240 --> 00:27:11,240
 otvoreni,

1006
00:27:11,240 --> 00:27:11,800
 dođi vamo,

1007
00:27:11,800 --> 00:27:12,420
 dođi tamo,

1008
00:27:12,420 --> 00:27:14,160
 i u to vrijeme

1009
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:15,380
 zaručnik od moje rodice

1010
00:27:15,380 --> 00:27:16,520
 je bio vozač Dondamiru.

1011
00:27:16,520 --> 00:27:17,880
 Znači, Dondamir naš putuje

1012
00:27:17,880 --> 00:27:18,500
 vamo i tamo

1013
00:27:18,500 --> 00:27:19,860
 po cijeloj Hrvatskoj Europi,

1014
00:27:19,860 --> 00:27:21,240
 i moj vozač da malo pomogne,

1015
00:27:21,240 --> 00:27:23,040
 i kako su se oni ženili,

1016
00:27:23,620 --> 00:27:24,800
 nije mu više mogao biti vozač.

1017
00:27:24,800 --> 00:27:25,640
 Kaže ovaj,

1018
00:27:25,640 --> 00:27:27,060
 kaže mene rodice,

1019
00:27:27,060 --> 00:27:27,960
 ma našta tomu,

1020
00:27:27,960 --> 00:27:29,460
 imam ti jednu predobru,

1021
00:27:29,460 --> 00:27:30,640
 predobru je stvar,

1022
00:27:30,640 --> 00:27:31,580
 kaže odobro šta reci,

1023
00:27:31,580 --> 00:27:33,120
 ma to ti je dobro,

1024
00:27:33,120 --> 00:27:33,580
 to ti je ne,

1025
00:27:33,580 --> 00:27:35,120
 ma dobro reci šta ma to,

1026
00:27:35,120 --> 00:27:36,900
 jer bi bio vozač

1027
00:27:36,900 --> 00:27:37,860
 Dondamiru Stoviću.

1028
00:27:37,860 --> 00:27:39,480
 Ja glavam šta vozač,

1029
00:27:39,480 --> 00:27:40,560
 kakav vozač ovaj,

1030
00:27:40,560 --> 00:27:41,680
 ja sam to puno studirao,

1031
00:27:41,680 --> 00:27:43,100
 ma bit će ti to super,

1032
00:27:43,100 --> 00:27:44,320
 putovaćeš vamo tamo,

1033
00:27:44,320 --> 00:27:45,200
 to ti je odlična prilika,

1034
00:27:45,200 --> 00:27:46,280
 to ti svi mladi žele,

1035
00:27:46,280 --> 00:27:48,080
 znači ovdje biti vozač

1036
00:27:48,080 --> 00:27:48,720
 Dondamiru Stoviću,

1037
00:27:48,720 --> 00:27:50,000
 moraš to kao prihvatiti.

1038
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:51,660
 Ja to prihvatim

1039
00:27:51,660 --> 00:27:53,380
 i stvarno istinu govorila,

1040
00:27:53,380 --> 00:27:53,880
 bilo mi jako...

1041
00:27:53,880 --> 00:27:54,660
 To su, oprosti,

1042
00:27:54,660 --> 00:27:55,400
 bilo su, dakle,

1043
00:27:55,400 --> 00:27:56,920
 vozač kada Dondamir ide na,

1044
00:27:56,920 --> 00:27:59,000
 Dondamir ide na evangelizaciji,

1045
00:27:59,000 --> 00:27:59,180
 slično.

1046
00:27:59,180 --> 00:28:00,420
 Tako je, tako je,

1047
00:28:00,420 --> 00:28:02,260
 ići s njim na te duhovne obnove,

1048
00:28:02,260 --> 00:28:02,760
 pomoći mu,

1049
00:28:02,760 --> 00:28:03,680
 to nije samo vožnje,

1050
00:28:03,680 --> 00:28:04,580
 još neke druge stvari,

1051
00:28:04,580 --> 00:28:05,360
 opomagati mu

1052
00:28:05,360 --> 00:28:07,300
 i bilo mi je stvarno lijepo,

1053
00:28:07,300 --> 00:28:09,140
 bilo mi jako lijepo

1054
00:28:09,140 --> 00:28:10,080
 s Dondamirom,

1055
00:28:10,080 --> 00:28:11,600
 postali smo jako dobri prijatelji

1056
00:28:11,600 --> 00:28:13,760
 i tako jedne večere

1057
00:28:13,760 --> 00:28:14,700
 dok sam sada vraćao

1058
00:28:14,700 --> 00:28:16,000
 s jedne duhovne obnove,

1059
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:18,000
 on meni ponudi

1060
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:19,360
 da dođem živjeti sa stalezijancima.

1061
00:28:19,360 --> 00:28:20,860
 A to ti je meni bio ono,

1062
00:28:20,860 --> 00:28:22,140
 meni se crvena lampica pali,

1063
00:28:22,140 --> 00:28:23,700
 sad ćete on tamo ubacit

1064
00:28:23,700 --> 00:28:25,280
 da budeš i ti stalezijac,

1065
00:28:25,280 --> 00:28:26,600
 to znaje na te vaše trikove,

1066
00:28:26,600 --> 00:28:27,200
 on tamo kaže,

1067
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:27,640
 a dobro,

1068
00:28:27,640 --> 00:28:28,060
 daj mi raj,

1069
00:28:28,060 --> 00:28:28,800
 vidit ćemo pomalo.

1070
00:28:28,800 --> 00:28:29,900
 I on je baš bio uporan,

1071
00:28:29,900 --> 00:28:30,220
 on kaže,

1072
00:28:30,220 --> 00:28:31,260
 ajde dođi,

1073
00:28:31,260 --> 00:28:32,020
 vidi barem sobu.

1074
00:28:32,020 --> 00:28:33,880
 I on ti je mene dostao tamo

1075
00:28:33,880 --> 00:28:34,300
 na večer,

1076
00:28:34,300 --> 00:28:34,480
 ne znam,

1077
00:28:34,480 --> 00:28:35,220
 bilo je kasno,

1078
00:28:35,640 --> 00:28:36,600
 ko mene gore vodi,

1079
00:28:36,600 --> 00:28:38,160
 otvara on tu sobu,

1080
00:28:38,160 --> 00:28:39,060
 klanja,

1081
00:28:39,060 --> 00:28:39,940
 nije loša soba,

1082
00:28:39,940 --> 00:28:40,540
 ja mislio,

1083
00:28:40,540 --> 00:28:41,360
 ja mislio,

1084
00:28:41,360 --> 00:28:42,200
 bit će to nešto,

1085
00:28:42,200 --> 00:28:42,500
 naš,

1086
00:28:42,500 --> 00:28:42,660
 ono,

1087
00:28:42,660 --> 00:28:43,820
 samo zidovi i daske,

1088
00:28:43,820 --> 00:28:45,020
 dok na domni je loša soba,

1089
00:28:45,020 --> 00:28:46,340
 još tu bolje mi je tu

1090
00:28:46,340 --> 00:28:46,900
 nego u Dubravi,

1091
00:28:46,900 --> 00:28:47,580
 tamo daleko,

1092
00:28:47,580 --> 00:28:49,280
 ali opet meni je to bilo,

1093
00:28:49,280 --> 00:28:49,540
 naš,

1094
00:28:49,540 --> 00:28:50,280
 meni je bila važna

1095
00:28:50,280 --> 00:28:51,100
 moja nekako sloboda,

1096
00:28:51,100 --> 00:28:51,620
 ja sam bio ono,

1097
00:28:51,620 --> 00:28:52,820
 najstariji sin u obitelji,

1098
00:28:52,820 --> 00:28:54,140
 uvijek su mi ono,

1099
00:28:54,140 --> 00:28:54,660
 mogo sam,

1100
00:28:54,660 --> 00:28:56,320
 mogo sam šta god doću raditi,

1101
00:28:56,320 --> 00:28:57,160
 to je me nekako bilo,

1102
00:28:57,160 --> 00:28:57,560
 baš,

1103
00:28:57,560 --> 00:28:59,360
 bojao sam se tamo otići živjeti,

1104
00:28:59,360 --> 00:28:59,540
 naš,

1105
00:28:59,540 --> 00:29:00,220
 neke molitve,

1106
00:29:00,220 --> 00:29:00,640
 pravila,

1107
00:29:00,640 --> 00:29:01,160
 vamo tamo,

1108
00:29:01,160 --> 00:29:01,500
 kaže ja,

1109
00:29:01,500 --> 00:29:01,780
 dobro,

1110
00:29:01,780 --> 00:29:02,140
 Damire,

1111
00:29:02,140 --> 00:29:03,360
 razmislit ću ja malo,

1112
00:29:03,360 --> 00:29:03,920
 pa ću vidjeti,

1113
00:29:03,920 --> 00:29:04,360
 da mislim se,

1114
00:29:04,360 --> 00:29:05,260
 nema šanse da dođe,

1115
00:29:05,260 --> 00:29:06,340
 i Damir,

1116
00:29:06,340 --> 00:29:07,440
 Damir to skuži,

1117
00:29:07,440 --> 00:29:08,900
 ovako Damir me pogleda

1118
00:29:08,900 --> 00:29:09,220
 i kaže,

1119
00:29:09,220 --> 00:29:10,360
 meni,

1120
00:29:10,360 --> 00:29:12,520
 možeš ići

1121
00:29:12,520 --> 00:29:14,240
 i vraćati se kako doćeš,

1122
00:29:14,240 --> 00:29:15,260
 niko te ne kontrolira,

1123
00:29:15,260 --> 00:29:16,940
 ja mu dam ruku,

1124
00:29:16,940 --> 00:29:17,500
 kaže,

1125
00:29:17,500 --> 00:29:17,880
 vrijedi,

1126
00:29:17,880 --> 00:29:18,960
 i sutra dan je nam došao

1127
00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:19,520
 u selio,

1128
00:29:19,660 --> 00:29:21,440
 u selio kod salesijanaca,

1129
00:29:21,440 --> 00:29:22,600
 i tu je on dan,

1130
00:29:22,600 --> 00:29:23,560
 tu sam ja opoznao bolje,

1131
00:29:23,560 --> 00:29:24,240
 salesijance,

1132
00:29:24,240 --> 00:29:25,800
 salesijanski duh,

1133
00:29:25,800 --> 00:29:26,960
 karizmu i to sve ostalo,

1134
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:28,120
 i tako da stvarno sad vidim,

1135
00:29:28,120 --> 00:29:28,300
 evo,

1136
00:29:28,300 --> 00:29:29,340
 to je to,

1137
00:29:29,340 --> 00:29:31,100
 to je ono što je za mene,

1138
00:29:31,100 --> 00:29:32,660
 a sad što se tiče fratara,

1139
00:29:32,660 --> 00:29:34,100
 naravno i u mom slučaju,

1140
00:29:34,100 --> 00:29:35,360
 što je normalno,

1141
00:29:35,360 --> 00:29:36,180
 što je prirodno,

1142
00:29:36,180 --> 00:29:37,980
 da im nije bilo to možda,

1143
00:29:37,980 --> 00:29:39,600
 da su očekivali možda da ću biti,

1144
00:29:39,600 --> 00:29:39,880
 ovaj,

1145
00:29:39,880 --> 00:29:40,980
 fratara,

1146
00:29:40,980 --> 00:29:42,060
 ali to prihvatili su,

1147
00:29:42,060 --> 00:29:44,920
 meni je teže možda bilo malo tamo u Hercegovini,

1148
00:29:44,920 --> 00:29:45,340
 ovaj,

1149
00:29:49,660 --> 00:29:50,720
 to je li to naša vjera,

1150
00:29:50,720 --> 00:29:51,600
 ali to koji su to,

1151
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:52,360
 je li to katolički,

1152
00:29:52,360 --> 00:29:53,240
 ma je bako,

1153
00:29:53,240 --> 00:29:54,080
 to je naši su to,

1154
00:29:54,080 --> 00:29:55,140
 naši su to bako,

1155
00:29:55,140 --> 00:29:56,940
 i tako i sad ja naš ono,

1156
00:29:56,940 --> 00:29:58,760
 a ja otušao tamo položio prve zavete,

1157
00:29:58,760 --> 00:30:00,320
 sad čekaju tamo u selu baka,

1158
00:30:00,320 --> 00:30:00,960
 svi čekaju,

1159
00:30:00,960 --> 00:30:03,100
 dolazi fratara nakon zaveta,

1160
00:30:03,100 --> 00:30:04,660
 ja dolazim u kuću,

1161
00:30:04,660 --> 00:30:06,500
 naš se mako baka gleda cijelo vrijeme,

1162
00:30:06,500 --> 00:30:07,720
 nešto naš nije njoj,

1163
00:30:07,720 --> 00:30:08,780
 a šta je,

1164
00:30:08,780 --> 00:30:09,680
 šta je kaže baka,

1165
00:30:09,680 --> 00:30:11,260
 ma dobro moj tomo sve to,

1166
00:30:11,260 --> 00:30:11,920
 je go,

1167
00:30:11,920 --> 00:30:13,220
 gdje tebi habitat više,

1168
00:30:13,340 --> 00:30:14,440
 kažu ga staviti ovaj,

1169
00:30:14,440 --> 00:30:16,160
 tako je to malo bilo,

1170
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:17,560
 ali ovdje su nekako ovaj,

1171
00:30:17,560 --> 00:30:19,300
 privikli su se,

1172
00:30:19,300 --> 00:30:20,500
 navikli su se ovaj,

1173
00:30:20,500 --> 00:30:21,120
 tako da evo,

1174
00:30:21,120 --> 00:30:21,560
 dobro je,

1175
00:30:21,560 --> 00:30:22,440
 dobro je to sve ispalo.

1176
00:30:22,440 --> 00:30:24,240
 Može neko od vas dvojice reći,

1177
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:27,000
 koliko vam je bilo bitno za,

1178
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:28,100
 ok,

1179
00:30:28,100 --> 00:30:29,460
 za stalezijanca razumijem,

1180
00:30:29,460 --> 00:30:29,680
 ali,

1181
00:30:29,680 --> 00:30:32,180
 izabrali ste redovnički način života,

1182
00:30:32,180 --> 00:30:34,300
 ono što je meni bilo novost,

1183
00:30:34,300 --> 00:30:38,340
 je da opće kad neko se odluči za svećenički poziv,

1184
00:30:38,340 --> 00:30:41,280
 da bira između redovničkog poziva,

1185
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:43,720
 i ja to zovem diaceza,

1186
00:30:43,720 --> 00:30:45,380
 ne znam li postoji stručni naziv,

1187
00:30:45,380 --> 00:30:49,520
 i ako dobro pratim diaceza,

1188
00:30:49,520 --> 00:30:50,100
 to su,

1189
00:30:50,100 --> 00:30:50,500
 dakle,

1190
00:30:50,500 --> 00:30:52,600
 mi to zovemo župnici u pravilu,

1191
00:30:52,600 --> 00:30:52,840
 dakle,

1192
00:30:52,840 --> 00:30:54,660
 oni ne žive u zajednici,

1193
00:30:54,660 --> 00:30:57,160
 dok vi redovnici,

1194
00:30:57,160 --> 00:30:57,860
 salezijanci,

1195
00:30:57,860 --> 00:30:59,220
 fratri,

1196
00:30:59,220 --> 00:30:59,820
 isusovci,

1197
00:30:59,820 --> 00:31:01,080
 živite u zajednici.

1198
00:31:01,080 --> 00:31:01,940
 Ok,

1199
00:31:01,940 --> 00:31:03,660
 je li vam to bilo bitno?

1200
00:31:03,660 --> 00:31:06,120
 Kako vam je to ulogu odigralo?

1201
00:31:06,120 --> 00:31:07,360
 Evo,

1202
00:31:07,360 --> 00:31:09,400
 ili bi se mogli zamislit

1203
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:11,140
 u ovoj priči sa diacezom?

1204
00:31:11,540 --> 00:31:12,160
 je to lakše,

1205
00:31:12,160 --> 00:31:12,500
 teže,

1206
00:31:12,500 --> 00:31:13,220
 evo,

1207
00:31:13,220 --> 00:31:14,340
 može jedan samo kogod.

1208
00:31:14,340 --> 00:31:15,980
 Pa evo,

1209
00:31:15,980 --> 00:31:16,200
 mislim,

1210
00:31:16,200 --> 00:31:16,800
 sad lakše,

1211
00:31:16,800 --> 00:31:17,240
 teže,

1212
00:31:17,240 --> 00:31:18,360
 ali evo,

1213
00:31:18,360 --> 00:31:19,160
 u mom slučaju,

1214
00:31:19,160 --> 00:31:19,560
 nekako,

1215
00:31:19,560 --> 00:31:21,360
 ja sam uvijek osjećao u srcu

1216
00:31:21,360 --> 00:31:23,160
 jednu snažnu čežnju

1217
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:25,120
 za tim obiteljskim duhom,

1218
00:31:25,120 --> 00:31:25,920
 za jednom obitelji,

1219
00:31:25,920 --> 00:31:26,760
 za jednom zajednicom.

1220
00:31:26,880 --> 00:31:27,880
 tako da je to sigurno igralo

1221
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:29,260
 vrlo važnu ulogu,

1222
00:31:29,260 --> 00:31:31,360
 ali nije samo to kod redovništva,

1223
00:31:31,360 --> 00:31:32,460
 nego zapravo,

1224
00:31:32,460 --> 00:31:34,780
 ono što je najviše kod redovništva,

1225
00:31:34,780 --> 00:31:36,480
 da su redovnici oni koji žele

1226
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:39,580
 radikalno slijediti Isusa Krista.

1227
00:31:40,100 --> 00:31:41,540
 Tako da je to meni također

1228
00:31:41,540 --> 00:31:42,580
 jednu vrlo važnu ulogu

1229
00:31:42,580 --> 00:31:43,680
 igralo kod redovništva

1230
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:45,420
 i zato redovnici polažu

1231
00:31:45,420 --> 00:31:45,980
 zavijete,

1232
00:31:45,980 --> 00:31:47,220
 siromaštva,

1233
00:31:47,220 --> 00:31:49,080
 čistoće i poslušnosti,

1234
00:31:49,080 --> 00:31:50,820
 jer žele biti kao Isus.

1235
00:31:50,820 --> 00:31:51,480
 Tako da evo,

1236
00:31:51,480 --> 00:31:53,540
 to je mene jako posebno

1237
00:31:53,540 --> 00:31:54,640
 privuklo kod redovništva.

1238
00:31:54,640 --> 00:31:55,760
 Nasledovanje Krista,

1239
00:31:55,760 --> 00:31:56,820
 biti kao Isus,

1240
00:31:56,820 --> 00:31:58,420
 život u zajednici,

1241
00:31:58,420 --> 00:31:59,080
 sa braćom

1242
00:31:59,080 --> 00:32:00,300
 i naravno naše poslanje

1243
00:32:00,300 --> 00:32:01,440
 koje imamo misle zjanci,

1244
00:32:01,440 --> 00:32:03,460
 a to su mladi.

1245
00:32:03,460 --> 00:32:04,820
 Ajmo sad to mrvo razlomit

1246
00:32:04,820 --> 00:32:05,700
 za nas lajke.

1247
00:32:05,700 --> 00:32:09,060
 Poslušnost,

1248
00:32:09,060 --> 00:32:10,100
 to mi je jasno,

1249
00:32:10,100 --> 00:32:12,020
 čistoća to mi je jasno,

1250
00:32:12,020 --> 00:32:13,800
 siromaštvo,

1251
00:32:13,800 --> 00:32:14,280
 frano,

1252
00:32:14,280 --> 00:32:15,740
 kaj to znači u praksi?

1253
00:32:15,740 --> 00:32:16,860
 Je li imaš plaću

1254
00:32:16,860 --> 00:32:17,480
 a nemaš plaću?

1255
00:32:17,480 --> 00:32:18,540
 Nemam plaću.

1256
00:32:18,540 --> 00:32:19,100
 Živote.

1257
00:32:19,100 --> 00:32:22,640
 Je li imaš išta na,

1258
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:24,480
 je li smiješ imati

1259
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:25,320
 išta na svoje ime?

1260
00:32:25,320 --> 00:32:26,720
 Ne.

1261
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:27,740
 Smiješ imati auto na svoje ime?

1262
00:32:27,740 --> 00:32:27,960
 Ne.

1263
00:32:27,960 --> 00:32:28,900
 Ne.

1264
00:32:28,900 --> 00:32:30,360
 A kajak si ga imao,

1265
00:32:30,360 --> 00:32:31,640
 propičeš ga nekom drugom?

1266
00:32:31,640 --> 00:32:32,340
 Dam ga,

1267
00:32:32,340 --> 00:32:33,480
 tako je.

1268
00:32:33,480 --> 00:32:34,760
 Dam ga obitelji

1269
00:32:34,760 --> 00:32:35,360
 ili dam u zajednici.

1270
00:32:35,360 --> 00:32:36,460
 I kak sam to funkcionira,

1271
00:32:38,020 --> 00:32:39,620
 ja se šišam svaka tri dana.

1272
00:32:39,620 --> 00:32:40,560
 Dobro.

1273
00:32:40,560 --> 00:32:41,520
 Što se vidi iz moje frizure.

1274
00:32:41,520 --> 00:32:42,400
 Ja se sam šišaš.

1275
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:42,680
 Dobro.

1276
00:32:42,680 --> 00:32:43,840
 Ok, ja se sam šišam,

1277
00:32:43,840 --> 00:32:44,320
 ali evo,

1278
00:32:44,320 --> 00:32:47,200
 treba mi 30 euro za mašinicu.

1279
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:47,860
 Koga ja pitam to?

1280
00:32:47,860 --> 00:32:48,700
 Dakle,

1281
00:32:48,700 --> 00:32:49,520
 svaka zajednica

1282
00:32:49,520 --> 00:32:50,560
 ima svoga

1283
00:32:50,560 --> 00:32:51,880
 takozvanog ekonoma,

1284
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:52,940
 jednoga brata,

1285
00:32:53,580 --> 00:32:55,240
 koji ima zadaću

1286
00:32:55,240 --> 00:32:57,020
 voditi financije zajednice

1287
00:32:57,020 --> 00:32:58,540
 i brinuti se

1288
00:32:58,540 --> 00:33:00,440
 za cijelu tu praktičnu stranu

1289
00:33:00,440 --> 00:33:01,180
 našeg života.

